      "content": "it's not just being \"overwhelmed.\" it feels more like i'm already dead and i just haven't realized it yet. like every single thing that made life worth living is just gone. everyone says it gets better, but how can it? the person who made me *me* is gone. there isn't a version of the future where i'm okay. it's just empty.",
