    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there's no \"navigating\" this. you don't navigate a void. it's just a permanent darkness. even if i talk to someone, or stay with family, it won't bring them back. the emptiness is all there is now. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen so the hurting will actually stop.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
